        public OccurrenceParseResult<TemporalAccessor> parseRecordedDate(String year,
                                                                 String month,
                                                                 String day,
                                                                 String dateString,
                                                                 String dayOfYear)
        Three dates are provided:
        • year, month and day
        • dateString
        • year and dayOfYear

        Produces a single date at the best resolution possible, ignoring missing values.

        Years are verified to be before this year and after 1500.

        Returns:
        interpretation result, never null
